<lb n="2"/>cūṭi villavar nilaikeṭa maṉ<supplied reason="omitted">ṉa</supplied>var kulaitara Eṉai manna<unclear>va</unclear><supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied> Iriyaluṟṟiḻi tarat tikkaṉaittun=tan cakkara naṭātti <unclear>vi</unclear>
